ions-hong-kong-arts-hub-axes-ceo-searches-new?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3220765_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="e41196f8-04a2-11eb-88c7-25dcd0ae6080" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-bundle="article">西九文化区</a>和<a href="https://www.scmp.com/sport/hong-kong/article/3219932/hong-kong-quite-confident-kai-tak-sports-park-can-open-end-2024-time-2025-national-games?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3220765_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="0a882c1d-ac5c-42a9-8e58-097773b6c78b" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-bundle="article">启德体育园</a>，我们对延期开放、额外拨款或成本超支习以为常。很少有项目能在预算内按时完成。</p><p> Covid-19 带来了一场完美的风暴，但我们只能将其归咎于病毒。例如， <a href="https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/transport/article/2169199/decade-deaths-and-delays-worlds-longest-sea-crossing?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3220765_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="60a3bc50-1a87-4e70-9144-cfab49ac6493" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-bundle="article">港珠澳大桥</a>和<a href="https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/hong-kong-economy/article/2165217/delays-inflated-costs-and-legal-wrangles-have?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3220765_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="5b15f5d4-09e8-4de0-b9a1-9aa3d4d2985b" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-bundle="article">广深港高铁</a>早在疫情之前就已建成，均超预算，在分别推迟两年和三年后于 2018 年通车。我们应该超越方便的借口，检查为什么我们的项目很少按计划交付。 </p><div class="meter__linear relative" id="default-meter-page-views-11"><img width="auto" height="1" src="https://www.scmp.com/images/1x1.png" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="dm__l3"><hr class="vertical-line"><div class="dm__lw"><svg class="dm__l" height="24" viewBox="0 0 18 24" width="18" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><g style="stroke:#000;fill:none;fill-rule:evenodd;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-width:1.5"><rect height="13.5" rx="1.5" width="16.5" 